# CarbonMirror — API Key Configuration
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# This file is for DOCUMENTATION ONLY.
# CarbonMirror is a 100% client-side application.
# No server, no build step, no backend.
# Your API key is NEVER stored in this file at runtime.
#
# HOW TO USE YOUR GEMINI API KEY:
# 1. Open index.html in your browser
# 2. On the home screen, paste your Gemini API key in the "Gemini AI" input field
# 3. Click "Save Key" — it is stored in sessionStorage ONLY (cleared on tab close)
# 4. Navigate to the Nudge section and scan any action
#
# HOW TO GET A FREE GEMINI API KEY:
# Visit: https://makersuite.google.com/app/apikey
# The free tier supports 60 requests/minute — more than enough for this app.
#
# PRIVACY:
# - Your key is stored in sessionStorage (never in localStorage or cookies)
# - Your key is sent ONLY to: generativelanguage.googleapis.com
# - All carbon data is stored locally in localStorage on your device
# - Zero server-side collection of any kind

GEMINI_API_KEY=your_key_here
